ow much he has prayed, whether three or four cycles, then let him put aside his doubt and act upon what he is certain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/01\/two-prostrations-sujud-al-sahwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":17357,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Satan makes him remember the world in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, if one of you stands for prayer, Satan comes to distract him until he does not know how many cycles he has performed. When that happens to one of you, let him perform two prostrations\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39772,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/shaytan-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17357,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Devil comes to distract believers in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the call to prayer is announced, Satan turns his back and he passes wind to avoid hearing it. When the call is finished, he turns around until the call for commencement is announced and then\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/when-the-prophet-forgot-ablution\/","url_meta":{"origin":17357,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: When the Prophet forgot ablution for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The prayer had been prepared and the rows straightened, then the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to us. When he stood in his place of prayer, he remembered that he was in a state of ritual impurity (junub). The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/expiation-forget-to-pray\/","url_meta":{"origin":17357,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Expiation for forgetting to pray on time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets a prayer, let him pray it when he remembers. There is no expiation other than this.\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \"Perform prayer for My remembrance.\" (20:14) Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 597, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 684\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28177,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-eight-rakaat-forenoon\/","url_meta":{"origin":17357,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Duha: The Prophet prays eight cycles in forenoon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hani\u2019 reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace blessings be upon him, in the year of the liberation, and I found him taking a bath. When the Prophet finished his bath, he performed eight cycles of prayer, and that was in the forenoon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 357,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17357","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17357"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17357\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17357"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17357"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17357"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}